-= Scullery =-
You find yourself in a scullery. A typical one.

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is a closed gateway leading south. There is an open door leading east.


Actions: ['close door', 'drop frisbee', 'examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine gateway', 'go east', 'inventory', 'look', 'open gateway', 'put frisbee on counter']
Taken action:go east
---------
-= Attic =-
You're now in an attic.

You see an opened spherical locker close by. Empty! What kind of nightmare TextWorld is this?

There is an open door leading west. There is an exit to the south. Don't worry, it is unblocked.

There is a spherical keycard and an insect on the floor.

Actions: ['close door', 'close spherical locker', 'drop frisbee', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine insect', 'examine spherical keycard', 'examine spherical locker', 'go south', 'go west', 'insert frisbee into spherical locker', 'inventory', 'look', 'take insect', 'take spherical keycard']
Taken action:go south
---------
-= Vault =-
You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out an opened toolbox. The toolbox contains a latchkey. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.


Actions: ['close toolbox', 'drop frisbee', 'examine frisbee', 'examine latchkey', 'examine shelf', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'insert frisbee into toolbox', 'inventory', 'look', 'put frisbee on shelf', 'take latchkey from toolbox']
Taken action:take latchkey from toolbox

You find yourself in a scullery. A typical one.

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is an open gateway leading south. There is a closed door leading east.


Actions: ['close gateway', 'examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine gateway', 'go south', 'inventory', 'look', 'open door']
Taken action:examine door

You can make out an opened toolbox. Empty! What kind of nightmare TextWorld is this? You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

There is an insect on the floor.

Actions: ['close toolbox', 'drop spherical keycard', 'examine insect', 'examine shelf', 'examine spherical keycard', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'insert spherical keycard into toolbox', 'inventory', 'look', 'put spherical keycard on shelf', 'take insect']
Taken action:inventory

You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out an opened toolbox. The toolbox contains a spherical keycard. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

There is an insect on the floor.

You can make out an opened toolbox. The toolbox contains an insect and a spherical keycard. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.


Actions: ['close toolbox', 'examine insect', 'examine shelf', 'examine spherical keycard', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'inventory', 'look', 'take insect from toolbox', 'take spherical keycard from toolbox']
Taken action:examine spherical keycard

You can make out an opened toolbox. The toolbox contains an insect and a spherical keycard. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

There is a frisbee on the floor.

Actions: ['close toolbox', 'examine frisbee', 'examine insect', 'examine shelf', 'examine spherical keycard', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'inventory', 'look', 'take frisbee', 'take insect from toolbox', 'take spherical keycard from toolbox']
Taken action:close toolbox

-= Vault =-
You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out an opened toolbox. Empty! What kind of nightmare TextWorld is this? You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is a closed gateway leading south. There is a closed door leading east.

There is an insect on the floor.

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is an open gateway leading south. There is an open door leading east.

There is a frisbee on the floor.

Actions: ['close door', 'close gateway', 'examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine gateway', 'go east', 'go south', 'inventory', 'look', 'take frisbee']
Taken action:close gateway

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is an open gateway leading south. There is an open door leading east.

There is a spherical keycard and a frisbee on the floor.

Actions: ['close door', 'close gateway', 'drop insect', 'examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine gateway', 'examine insect', 'examine spherical keycard', 'go east', 'go south', 'inventory', 'look', 'put insect on counter', 'take frisbee', 'take spherical keycard']
Taken action:examine counter

-= Vault =-
You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out an opened toolbox. Empty! What kind of nightmare TextWorld is this? You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.


Actions: ['close toolbox', 'examine shelf', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'inventory', 'look']
Taken action:close toolbox

You find yourself in a scullery. A typical one.

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. You see a spherical keycard on the counter.

There is an open gateway leading south. There is a closed door leading east.

There is a frisbee on the floor.

Actions: ['close gateway', 'drop insect', 'drop latchkey', 'examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine gateway', 'examine insect', 'examine latchkey', 'examine spherical keycard', 'go south', 'inventory', 'look', 'open door', 'put insect on counter', 'put latchkey on counter', 'take frisbee', 'take spherical keycard from counter']
Taken action:drop insect

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is a closed gateway leading south. There is an open door leading east.

There is an insect on the floor.

Actions: ['close door', 'drop frisbee', 'drop spherical keycard', 'examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine gateway', 'examine insect', 'examine spherical keycard', 'go east', 'inventory', 'look', 'open gateway', 'put frisbee on counter', 'put spherical keycard on counter', 'take insect']
Taken action:go east

-= Vault =-
You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out an opened toolbox. The toolbox contains a latchkey. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is an open gateway leading south. There is an open door leading east.

There is a type Z passkey and an insect on the floor.

Taken action:examine gateway

You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out a closed toolbox. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

You're now in an attic.

You see a locked spherical locker close by.

There is an open door leading west. There is an exit to the south. Don't worry, it is unblocked.

There is a frisbee on the floor.

Actions: ['close door', 'drop insect', 'drop type Z passkey', 'examine door', 'examine frisbee', 'examine insect', 'examine spherical locker', 'examine type Z passkey', 'go south', 'go west', 'inventory', 'look', 'take frisbee']
Taken action:go south
---------
-= Vault =-
You find yourself in a vault. A typical kind of place.

You can make out an opened toolbox. The toolbox contains a latchkey. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

There is a spherical keycard on the floor.

Taken action:put type Z passkey on shelf

-= Vault =-

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

You can make out a closed toolbox. You can make out a shelf. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a shelf? However, the shelf, like an empty shelf, has nothing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the shelf.

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.

There is a latchkey on the floor.

Actions: ['examine latchkey', 'examine shelf', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'inventory', 'look', 'open toolbox', 'take latchkey']
Taken action:examine toolbox

You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is unblocked.


Actions: ['close toolbox', 'drop latchkey', 'drop spherical keycard', 'examine latchkey', 'examine shelf', 'examine spherical keycard', 'examine toolbox', 'go north', 'insert latchkey into toolbox', 'insert spherical keycard into toolbox', 'inventory', 'look', 'put latchkey on shelf', 'put spherical keycard on shelf']
Taken action:put latchkey on shelf

You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. The counter appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter.

There is a closed gateway leading south. There is a closed door leading east.


Actions: ['examine counter', 'examine door', 'examine gateway', 'inventory', 'look', 'open door', 'open gateway']
Taken action:examine gateway
